cial \"Grand Battle Dungeons\" that allow you to construct a deck to challenge with</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 50 random events featuring various game characters, real and imagined</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Daily and weekly dungeon challenges with online leaderboards</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Real-time online head-to-head battles</li></ul>",
